data.description: Step into this charming 3-bed, 2-bath home nestled in a peaceful neighborhood. This Home has a spacious living area, ideal for family gatherings, and a well-appointed kitchen with modern appliances. Enjoy the comfort of a master suite with a private bath, while two additional bedrooms provide flexibility for guests or a home office. The beautifully landscaped backyard is perfect for outdoor relaxation. Conveniently located near schools, parks, and shopping, this home is a wonderful blend of comfort and convenience. Book you're showing today!
